{"parse":{"title":"Writing fellow","pageid":6274974,"revid":604309064,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <b>Writing Fellow</b> or <b>Fellow in Writing</b> is a tutor or <a href=\"/wiki/Consultant\" title=\"Consultant\">consultant</a> who assists with <a href=\"/wiki/College\" title=\"College\">college</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/University\" title=\"University\">university</a> writing instruction in specific <a href=\"/wiki/Academic_major\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Academic major\">courses</a> or academic fields. Whereas most <a href=\"/wiki/Writing_Center\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Writing Center\">Writing Center</a> tutors are generalists, ready to work with writing from any course or field, Writing Fellows are specialists. Often working within a Writing Center or Writing Across a Curriculum program, they typically provide oral and/or written feedback on papers to students in an upper-division writing class. A Writing Fellow is most often a <a href=\"/wiki/Peer_tutor\" title=\"Peer tutor\">peer tutor</a>; however, the term \u201cWriting Fellow\u201d is also sometimes used for faculty members who advise others on teaching, assigning and responding to student writing in their specific disciplines.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Writing_fellow&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Writing_Center\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Writing Center\">Writing Center</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Composition_studies\" title=\"Composition studies\">Composition studies</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Writing_fellow&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://wac.colostate.edu/atd/fellows/index.cfm\">Special issue of <i>Across the Disciplines</i> on Rewriting Across the Curriculum: Writing Fellows as Agents of Change in WAC</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.barnard.edu/writing/writingcenter.html\">Barnard College Writing Fellows Program</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.brown.edu/Student_Services/Writing_Fellows/\">Brown University Writing Fellows</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ccny.cuny.edu/wac/\">The City College Writing Fellows Program</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.falmouth.ac.uk/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=view&amp;id=304&amp;Itemid=142\">University College Falmouth Writing Fellows</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://wac.colostate.edu/fellows/\">Writing Across the Curriculum Clearinghouse--List of Writing Fellows Programs</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.wisc.edu/writing/wf/main.html\">University of Wisconsin-Madison Undergraduate Writing Fellows Program</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://writing.rochester.edu/writing_fellows/index.html\">University of Rochester Writing Fellows Program</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/bewritemit/\">MIT's Department of Biological Engineering, Writing Fellow Program</a></li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"metadata plainlinks stub\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:transparent\"><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Nuvola_apps_bookcase.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stub icon\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a